name: Pachinko & Pachi-Slot: Parlor! Pro EX: CR Inakappe Taishou A & Pachi-Slot Lupin Sansei
overview: Pachinko & Pachi-Slot Parlor! Pro Extra is a pachi-slot (gambling machine) game that features a perfect recreation of 2 gambling machines (Inakappe Taishou Special Pachinko & Lupin Pachi-Slot) with different levels of zoom.
